    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Indigenous, traditional religious beliefs and practices of the peoples of Africa south of the Sahara, which are not homogeneous across cultures but share certain commonalities in world view.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
